Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2026-02-19",
  "flow": "heavy"
}

### ===============================
### 2️⃣ Log Daily Flow
POST {{baseUrl}}/period/log-day
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-02-20",
  "flow": "medium"
}

### ===============================
### 3️⃣ Log Another Day
POST {{baseUrl}}/period/log-day
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-02-21",
  "flow": "light"
}

### ===============================
### 4️⃣ End Period
POST {{baseUrl}}/period/end
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endDate": "2026-02-24"
}

### ===============================
### 5️⃣ Get Period History
GET {{baseUrl}}/period/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===============================
### 6️⃣ Get Next Period Prediction
GET {{baseUrl}}/period/prediction
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
